<testcase>
<info>
<keywords>
HTTP
HTTP POST
HTTP Digest auth
</keywords>
</info>

# Server-side
<reply>
<data>
HTTP/1.1 401 authentication please swsbounce
Server: Microsoft-IIS/6.0
